title: Inner Earth and Sun
description: An artistic representation showing a cross-section of the Earth with the molten core and the sun above. The Earth's surface is visible with continents and oceans, while the inner layers depict the fiery core and magma.

title: Cross-Section of Celestial Bodies
description: An illustration showing the cross-sections of various celestial bodies, including a small asteroid, a planet with a solid outer layer and a molten core, and a larger planet with a distinct inner core. The cores are depicted in red, indicating heat or molten material, while the outer layers are shown in gray, representing solid rock.

title: Geographical View of the Iberian Peninsula
description: A digital rendering of the Iberian Peninsula, showcasing its geographical features. The image highlights the landmass of Spain and Portugal, surrounded by the Mediterranean Sea and the Atlantic Ocean. The depiction includes a three-dimensional perspective, emphasizing the contours and elevations of the terrain.

title: World Map
description: A detailed satellite image of the world, showing continents, oceans, and various geographical features. The map highlights the green and brown landmasses of continents like North America, South America, Europe, Africa, Asia, and Australia, surrounded by blue oceans.

title: Obsidian Rock
description: A rough, irregularly shaped piece of obsidian, a naturally occurring volcanic glass. The surface is dark and shiny with a textured appearance, featuring jagged edges and a glossy finish.
